{"tid":1330180,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"惡人先告狀 還原理大畢業生襲警事發經過","createTime":"2019-07-18T12:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T12:45:46.000Z","uid":158090,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"14f4ca91c6c9143c447a8af578766e76fef48140","tid":1330180,"uid":158090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T12:44:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞：<br />\n<br />\n一名應屆理工大學應屆畢業生，今日下午同樣在沙田裁判法院提堂，該名男子在沙田衝突現場被捕，案情指他被帶到警署後襲警，遭暫控三項襲警罪，獲准保釋。<br />\n<br />\n該名姓文的男子今日在沙田裁判法院提堂，裁判官批准案件押後處理，被告獲准保釋，保釋金為 1 萬元，另加 1 萬元人事擔保。<br />\n<br />\n男被告為理工大學旅遊及酒店管理系應屆畢業生，目前無業。控方案情指出，男被告在新城市廣場涉非法集結被捕，被帶到葵涌警署，在警署內用頭撞向第一名警員的額頭，用右手拳打第二名警員的臉頰，並用雙手抓傷第三名警員的手，被暫控三項襲警罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E5%85%A7%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6-%E6%8E%A7%E4%B8%89%E9%A0%85%E8%A5%B2%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E7%95%A2%E6%A5%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/?fbclid=IwAR3i266arN_M_GziOr6Y7V7Le6HQt4C_DsD52A3ZHfevSpAGpCAZnAaT1rQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E6%258E%25A7%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%25A0%2585%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2595%25A2%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3i266arN_M_GziOr6Y7V7Le6HQt4C_DsD52A3ZHfevSpAGpCAZnAaT1rQ&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHEwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=0f790fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0%25E8%25A1%259D%25E7%25AA%2581-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A5%25B2%